reviewText: This is not a great movie, but it's fun for fans of old movies like me.
Belita was the best ice skater ever....and a very good actress/dancer.  I have all of her movies.
Excellent Musical Dancing/Skating film. Print had good picture and sound.
Great Skating, and dancing..it was to bad MGM did not produce skating films for Belita,.... really no other talent like her.
